        "Creating the new manufacturing/delivery processes for the new products/services, and testing them to ensure proper functioning. 创建 the production/delivery process for the prototypes that have been built for the new products/services. 开展 trial-runs to test these processes and their integration with the organization's other processes."@zh ;
    skos:inScheme <https://oprocess.net/opf> ;
