        "Carrying out an in-house appraisal of the prototypes in order to validate design and feasibility. 测试 the product/service prototypes to confirm their 合规 with design and usability standards. Corroborate the viability of the design, and validate the feasibility of their production. 识别 any areas for improvement."@zh ;
    skos:inScheme <https://oprocess.net/opf> ;
    skos:notation "2.3.1.12" ;
