<https://oprocess.net/opf/node/4.2.1.1> a skos:Concept,
        opf:ProcessNode ;
    dcterms:source "PCF:4.2.1.1" ;
    skos:broader <https://oprocess.net/opf/node/4.2.1> ;
    skos:definition "Creating a plan for procuring materials and services. Plan what to buy, when, and from what sources. Include project requirements, the procurement team, the justification for the procurement, a timeline of events, and an explanation of the supplier selection process. Outline specific actions to start and complete purchases in order to adhere to best practices."@en,
        "Creating a plan for procuring materials and services. 规划 what to buy, when, and from what sources. Include project requirements, the procurement team, the justification for the procurement, a timeline of events, and an explanation of the supplier selection process. Outline specific actions to start and complete purchases in order to adhere to best practices."@zh ;
    skos:inScheme <https://oprocess.net/opf> ;
    skos:notation "4.2.1.1" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Develop procurement plan"@en,
        "开发 procurement plan"@zh ;
    opf:domain "operating" ;
    opf:level 4 .

<https://oprocess.net/opf/node/4.2.1.2> a skos:Concept,
        opf:ProcessNode ;
    dcterms:source "PCF:4.2.1.2" ;
    skos:broader <https://oprocess.net/opf/node/4.2.1> ;
    skos:definition "Defining the purchasing requirements for materials and services. Specify the exact inventory required for the production process. Create a specific quotation for all the sources in order to avoid any duplication or overlap."@en,
        "Defining the purchasing requirements for materials and services. Specify the exact inventory required for the production process. 创建 a specific quotation for all the sources in order to avoid any duplication or overlap."@zh ;
    skos:inScheme <https://oprocess.net/opf> ;
    skos:notation "4.2.1.2" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Clarify purchasing requirements"@en ;
    opf:domain "operating" ;
    opf:level 4 .

<https://oprocess.net/opf/node/4.2.1.3> a skos:Concept,
        opf:ProcessNode ;
    dcterms:source "PCF:4.2.1.3" ;
    skos:broader <https://oprocess.net/opf/node/4.2.1> ;
    skos:definition "Developing a strategy to deal with issues projected to arise during implementation of the inventory plan. Identify how to react to issues that arise and require changes to the inventory plan, such as a vendor failing to deliver materials on time. Collaborate with production and suppliers to prepare solutions to projected problems."@en,
        "Developing a 战略 to deal with issues projected to arise during implementation of the inventory plan. 识别 how to react to issues that arise and require 变更s to the inventory plan, such as a vendor failing to deliver materials on time. Collaborate with production and suppliers to prepare solutions to projected 问题s."@zh ;
    skos:inScheme <https://oprocess.net/opf> ;
    skos:notation "4.2.1.3" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Establish materials management contingency plans"@en,
        "建立 materials management contingency plans"@zh ;
    opf:domain "operating" ;
    opf:level 4 .

<https://oprocess.net/opf/node/4.2.1.4> a skos:Concept,
        opf:ProcessNode ;
    dcterms:source "PCF:4.2.1.4" ;
    skos:broader <https://oprocess.net/opf/node/4.2.1> ;
    skos:definition "Synchronizing the requirements of materials and services and the capacity of suppliers for providing these materials and services. Revamp the procurement needs of the company in consideration of the capabilities of the suppliers."@en,
        "Synchronizing the requirements of materials and services and the 容量 of suppliers for providing these materials and services. Revamp the procurement needs of the company in consideration of the capabilities of the suppliers."@zh ;
    skos:inScheme <https://oprocess.net/opf> ;
    skos:notation "4.2.1.4" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Match needs to supply capabilities"@en ;
    opf:domain "operating" ;
    opf:level 4 .

<https://oprocess.net/opf/node/4.2.1.5> a skos:Concept,
        opf:ProcessNode ;
    dcterms:source "PCF:4.2.1.5" ;
    skos:broader <https://oprocess.net/opf/node/4.2.1> ;
    skos:definition "Evaluating the spend profile of the organization. Collect, cleanse, classify, and analyze the procurement data with the purpose of reducing procurement costs, improving efficiency, and monitoring compliance."@en,
        "Evaluating the spend profile of the organization. 收集, cleanse, classify, and analyze the procurement data with the purpose of reducing procurement costs, improving efficiency, and 监控 合规."@zh ;
    skos:inScheme <https://oprocess.net/opf> ;
    skos:notation "4.2.1.5" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Analyze organization’s spend profile"@en,
        "分析 organization’s spend profile"@zh ;
    opf:domain "operating" ;
    opf:level 4 .

<https://oprocess.net/opf/node/4.2.1.6> a skos:Concept,
        opf:ProcessNode ;
    dcterms:source "PCF:4.2.1.6" ;
    skos:broader <https://oprocess.net/opf/node/4.2.1> ;
    skos:definition "Seeking the most efficient sourcing and procurement opportunities."@en ;
    skos:inScheme <https://oprocess.net/opf> ;
    skos:notation "4.2.1.6" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Seek opportunities to improve efficiency and value"@en ;
    opf:domain "operating" ;
    opf:level 4 .

<https://oprocess.net/opf/node/4.2.1.7> a skos:Concept,
        opf:ProcessNode ;
    dcterms:source "PCF:4.2.1.7" ;
    skos:broader <https://oprocess.net/opf/node/4.2.1> ;
    skos:definition "Collaborating with the suppliers of materials and services in order to determine new opportunities for sourcing, share market insights, manage risk, identify and align supplier capabilities with long-term business goals."@en,
        "Collaborating with the suppliers of materials and services in order to determine new opportunities for sourcing, share market insights, manage 风险, identify and align supplier capabilities with long-term business goals."@zh ;
    skos:inScheme <https://oprocess.net/opf> ;
    skos:notation "4.2.1.7" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Collaborate with suppliers to align with long term business goals"@en ;
    opf:domain "operating" ;
    opf:level 4 .

<https://oprocess.net/opf/node/4.2.1.8> a skos:Concept,
        opf:ProcessNode ;
    dcterms:source "PCF:4.2.1.8" ;
    skos:broader <https://oprocess.net/opf/node/4.2.1> ;
    skos:definition "Collaborating with the suppliers of materials and services in order to determine new opportunities for sourcing."@en ;
    skos:inScheme <https://oprocess.net/opf> ;
    skos:notation "4.2.1.8" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Collaborate with suppliers to identify sourcing opportunities"@en ;
    opf:domain "operating" ;
    opf:level 4 .

<https://oprocess.net/opf/node/4.2.2.1> a skos:Concept,
        opf:ProcessNode ;
    dcterms:source "PCF:4.2.2.1" ;
    skos:broader <https://oprocess.net/opf/node/4.2.2> ;
    skos:definition "Analyzing the position and performance of sourcing categories or products based on spend, supplier dynamics, market conditions, and value contribution to inform category planning decisions."@en,
        "Analyzing the position and 绩效 of sourcing categories or products based on spend, supplier dynamics, market conditions, and value contribution to inform category planning decisions."@zh ;
    skos:inScheme <https://oprocess.net/opf> ;
    skos:notation "4.2.2.1" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Analyze category/product positioning and performance"@en,
        "分析 category/product positioning and 绩效"@zh ;
    opf:domain "operating" ;
    opf:level 4 .

<https://oprocess.net/opf/node/4.2.2.2> a skos:Concept,
        opf:ProcessNode ;
    dcterms:source "PCF:4.2.2.2" ;
    skos:broader <https://oprocess.net/opf/node/4.2.2> ;
    skos:definition "Forecasting demand for sourcing categories across relevant markets or consumption channels to support planning, supplier strategy, and capacity alignment."@en,
        "Forecasting demand for sourcing categories across relevant markets or consumption channels to support planning, supplier 战略, and 容量 对齐."@zh ;
    skos:inScheme <https://oprocess.net/opf> ;
    skos:notation "4.2.2.2" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Forecast demand for each category by market"@en,
        "预测 demand for each category by market"@zh ;
    opf:domain "operating" ;
    opf:level 4 .

<https://oprocess.net/opf/node/4.2.2.3> a skos:Concept,
        opf:ProcessNode ;
    dcterms:source "PCF:4.2.2.3" ;
    skos:broader <https://oprocess.net/opf/node/4.2.2> ;
    skos:definition "Establishing revenue, cost, and margin targets for sourcing categories to guide category strategy, sourcing decisions, and performance evaluation."@en,
        "Establishing revenue, cost, and margin targets for sourcing categories to guide category 战略, sourcing decisions, and 绩效 evaluation."@zh ;
    skos:inScheme <https://oprocess.net/opf> ;
    skos:notation "4.2.2.3" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Assign revenue and margin targets to each category"@en ;
    opf:domain "operating" ;
    opf:level 4 .

<https://oprocess.net/opf/node/4.2.3.1> a skos:Concept,
        opf:ProcessNode ;
    dcterms:source "PCF:4.2.3.1" ;
    skos:broader <https://oprocess.net/opf/node/4.2.3> ;
    skos:definition "Evaluating the pros and cons of various suppliers. Choose the most appropriate and cost-effective suppliers on the basis of their material quality, delivery schedules, and costs."@en,
        "Evaluating the pros and cons of various suppliers. Choose the most appropriate and cost-effective suppliers on the basis of their material 质量, delivery schedules, and costs."@zh ;
    skos:inScheme <https://oprocess.net/opf> ;
    skos:notation "4.2.3.1" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Select suppliers"@en,
        "选择 suppliers"@zh ;
    opf:domain "operating" ;
    opf:level 4 .

<https://oprocess.net/opf/node/4.2.3.2> a skos:Concept,
        opf:ProcessNode ;
    dcterms:source "PCF:4.2.3.2" ;
    skos:broader <https://oprocess.net/opf/node/4.2.3> ;
    skos:definition "Validating the supply sources, and provide certification as an official supplier."@en ;
    skos:inScheme <https://oprocess.net/opf> ;
    skos:notation "4.2.3.2" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Certify and validate suppliers"@en ;
    opf:domain "operating" ;
    opf:level 4 .

<https://oprocess.net/opf/node/4.2.3.3> a skos:Concept,
        opf:ProcessNode ;
    dcterms:source "PCF:4.2.3.3" ;
    skos:broader <https://oprocess.net/opf/node/4.2.3> ;
    skos:definition "Legally binding suppliers with the company. Negotiate contracts individually with all the suppliers that include the promised material delivery, the delivery dates and duration, etc."@en ;
    skos:inScheme <https://oprocess.net/opf> ;
    skos:notation "4.2.3.3" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Negotiate and establish contracts"@en ;
    opf:domain "operating" ;
    opf:level 4 .

<https://oprocess.net/opf/node/4.2.3.4> a skos:Concept,
        opf:ProcessNode ;
    dcterms:source "PCF:4.2.3.4" ;
    skos:broader <https://oprocess.net/opf/node/4.2.3> ;
    skos:definition "Keeping contracts up-to-date with routine evaluation. Maintain order and discipline with the contracts in order to avoid any loss of information and mishaps."@en,
        "Keeping contracts up-to-date with routine evaluation. 维护 order and discipline with the contracts in order to avoid any loss of information and mishaps."@zh ;
    skos:inScheme <https://oprocess.net/opf> ;
    skos:notation "4.2.3.4" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Manage contracts"@en,
        "管理 contracts"@zh ;
    opf:domain "operating" ;
    opf:level 4 .

<https://oprocess.net/opf/node/4.2.4.1> a skos:Concept,
        opf:ProcessNode ;
    dcterms:source "PCF:4.2.4.1" ;
    skos:broader <https://oprocess.net/opf/node/4.2.4> ;
    skos:definition "Handling operations related to processing/reviewing the requisitions. Establish and maintain procedures for the initiation, authorization, and processing of purchase requirements to procure products/services."@en,
        "Handling operations related to processing/reviewing the requisitions. 建立 and maintain procedures for the initiation, authorization, and processing of purchase requirements to procure products/services."@zh ;
    skos:inScheme <https://oprocess.net/opf> ;
    skos:notation "4.2.4.1" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Process/Review requisitions"@en,
        "处理/审查 requisitions"@zh ;
    opf:domain "operating" ;
    opf:level 4 .

<https://oprocess.net/opf/node/4.2.4.2> a skos:Concept,
        opf:ProcessNode ;
    dcterms:source "PCF:4.2.4.2" ;
    skos:broader <https://oprocess.net/opf/node/4.2.4> ;
    skos:definition "Approving requisitions for materials and services. Examine distributor-specific requests, and validate them individually."@en ;
    skos:inScheme <https://oprocess.net/opf> ;
    skos:notation "4.2.4.2" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Approve requisitions"@en ;
    opf:domain "operating" ;
    opf:level 4 .

<https://oprocess.net/opf/node/4.2.4.3> a skos:Concept,
        opf:ProcessNode ;
    dcterms:source "PCF:4.2.4.3" ;
    skos:broader <https://oprocess.net/opf/node/4.2.4> ;
    skos:definition "Requesting quotes from suppliers. Use a request for quotation (RFQ) to invite suppliers into a bidding process for specific products/services."@en ;
    skos:inScheme <https://oprocess.net/opf> ;
    skos:notation "4.2.4.3" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Solicit supplier quotes"@en ;
    opf:domain "operating" ;
    opf:level 4 .

<https://oprocess.net/opf/node/4.2.4.4> a skos:Concept,
        opf:ProcessNode ;
    dcterms:source "PCF:4.2.4.4" ;
    skos:broader <https://oprocess.net/opf/node/4.2.4> ;
    skos:definition "Creating and placing the orders for purchasing materials and services from suppliers. Analyze vendor quotes. Choose the most cost-effective vendors. Create vendor-specific orders. Distribute them in order to initiate the purchasing process."@en,
        "Creating and placing the orders for purchasing materials and services from suppliers. 分析 vendor quotes. Choose the most cost-effective vendors. 创建 vendor-specific orders. Distribute them in order to initiate the purchasing process."@zh ;
    skos:inScheme <https://oprocess.net/opf> ;
    skos:notation "4.2.4.4" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Create/Distribute purchase orders"@en,
        "创建/Distribute purchase orders"@zh ;
    opf:domain "operating" ;
    opf:level 4 .

<https://oprocess.net/opf/node/4.2.4.5> a skos:Concept,
        opf:ProcessNode ;
    dcterms:source "PCF:4.2.4.5" ;
    skos:broader <https://oprocess.net/opf/node/4.2.4> ;
    skos:definition "Accelerating the purchase orders in order to fulfill the internal needs (for raw materials) depicted through inquiries."@en,
        "Accelerating the purchase orders in order to 履约 the internal needs (for raw materials) depicted through inquiries."@zh ;
    skos:inScheme <https://oprocess.net/opf> ;
    skos:notation "4.2.4.5" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Expedite orders and satisfy inquiries"@en ;
    opf:domain "operating" ;
    opf:level 4 .

<https://oprocess.net/opf/node/4.2.4.6> a skos:Concept,
        opf:ProcessNode ;
    dcterms:source "PCF:4.2.4.6" ;
    skos:broader <https://oprocess.net/opf/node/4.2.4> ;
    skos:definition "Verify that purchase orders are filled as expected: verify that items and quantities are delivered as expected, based on purchase order details and goods receipts."@en,
        "验证 that purchase orders are filled as expected: verify that items and quantities are delivered as expected, based on purchase order details and goods receipts."@zh ;
    skos:inScheme <https://oprocess.net/opf> ;
    skos:notation "4.2.4.6" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Reconcile purchase orders"@en ;
    opf:domain "operating" ;
    opf:level 4 .

<https://oprocess.net/opf/node/4.2.4.7> a skos:Concept,
        opf:ProcessNode ;
    dcterms:source "PCF:4.2.4.7" ;
    skos:broader <https://oprocess.net/opf/node/4.2.4> ;
    skos:definition "Identifying and resolving any exceptions. Address the internal needs/inquiries for materials that cannot be procured immediately. Research inquiries that require the need of exceptional materials."@en ;
    skos:inScheme <https://oprocess.net/opf> ;
    skos:notation "4.2.4.7" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Research/Resolve order exceptions"@en,
        "Research/解决 order exceptions"@zh ;
    opf:domain "operating" ;
    opf:level 4 .

<https://oprocess.net/opf/node/4.2.5.1> a skos:Concept,
        opf:ProcessNode ;
    dcterms:source "PCF:4.2.5.1" ;
    skos:broader <https://oprocess.net/opf/node/4.2.5> ;
    skos:definition "Create and maintain vendor master files. Examining procurement and vendor performance. Report delivery timing and the quality of the materials procured through different vendors.  This data must align with vendor master file, see PCFID 10869."@en,
        "创建 and maintain vendor master files. Examining procurement and vendor 绩效. 报告 delivery timing and the 质量 of the materials procured through different vendors.  This data must align with vendor master file, see PCFID 10869."@zh ;
    skos:inScheme <https://oprocess.net/opf> ;
    skos:notation "4.2.5.1" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Monitor/Manage supplier information"@en,
        "监控/管理 supplier information"@zh ;
    opf:domain "operating" ;
    opf:level 4 .

<https://oprocess.net/opf/node/4.2.5.2> a skos:Concept,
        opf:ProcessNode ;
    dcterms:source "PCF:4.2.5.2" ;
    skos:broader <https://oprocess.net/opf/node/4.2.5> ;
    skos:definition "Assisting the production and inventory processes through the information and reports created. Use the information and metrics of the procurement and vendor performance to enhance or improve the production process."@en,
        "Assisting the production and inventory processes through the information and reports created. Use the information and metrics of the procurement and vendor 绩效 to enhance or improve the production process."@zh ;
    skos:inScheme <https://oprocess.net/opf> ;
    skos:notation "4.2.5.2" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Prepare/Analyze procurement and supplier performance"@en,
        "准备/分析 procurement and supplier 绩效"@zh ;
    opf:domain "operating" ;
    opf:level 4 .

<https://oprocess.net/opf/node/4.2.5.3> a skos:Concept,
        opf:ProcessNode ;
    dcterms:source "PCF:4.2.5.3" ;
    skos:broader <https://oprocess.net/opf/node/4.2.5> ;
    skos:definition "Support inventory and production processes by analyzing impact of procurement decisions and collaborating to constantly improve. (For example, perhaps minimum order requirements could be negotiated to be lower, to reduce excessive inventory and make production more flexible.)"@en ;
    skos:inScheme <https://oprocess.net/opf> ;
    skos:notation "4.2.5.3" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Support inventory and production processes"@en ;
    opf:domain "operating" ;
    opf:level 4 .

<https://oprocess.net/opf/node/4.2.5.4> a skos:Concept,
        opf:ProcessNode ;
    dcterms:source "PCF:4.2.5.4" ;
    skos:broader <https://oprocess.net/opf/node/4.2.5> ;
    skos:definition "Track the performance of the suppliers on product quality. Use this information to further improve sourcing and supplier performance."@en,
        "跟踪 the 绩效 of the suppliers on product 质量. Use this information to further improve sourcing and supplier 绩效."@zh ;
    skos:inScheme <https://oprocess.net/opf> ;
    skos:notation "4.2.5.4" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Monitor quality of product delivered"@en,
        "监控 质量 of product delivered"@zh ;
    opf:domain "operating" ;
    opf:level 4 .

