        "AI-era activity: AI-Enabled 质量 Inspection."@zh ;
    skos:inScheme <https://oprocess.net/opf> ;
    skos:notation "4.3.8" ;
    skos:prefLabel "AI-Enabled Quality Inspection"@en,
        "AI-Enabled 质量 Inspection"@zh ;
    opf:domain "operating" ;
    opf:level 3 .

<https://oprocess.net/opf/node/4.4.1.1> a skos:Concept,
        opf:ProcessNode ;
    dcterms:source "PCF:4.4.1.1" ;
    skos:broader <https://oprocess.net/opf/node/4.4.1> ;
    skos:definition "Determining the requirements for managing the flow of things between the point of origin and the point of consumption by assessing the service requirements of the customers."@en ;
    skos:inScheme <https://oprocess.net/opf> ;
    skos:notation "4.4.1.1" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Translate customer service requirements into logistics requirements"@en,
        "Translate 客户服务 requirements into logistics requirements"@zh ;
    opf:domain "operating" ;
    opf:level 4 .

<https://oprocess.net/opf/node/4.4.1.2> a skos:Concept,
        opf:ProcessNode ;
    dcterms:source "PCF:4.4.1.2" ;
    skos:broader <https://oprocess.net/opf/node/4.4.1> ;
    skos:definition "Developing a network for logistical activities. Create a network of entities through which materials and information flow, encompassing all related activities associated with the flow of transformation of products."@en,
        "Developing a network for logistical activities. 创建 a network of entities through which materials and information flow, encompassing all related activities associated with the flow of 转化ation of products."@zh ;
    skos:inScheme <https://oprocess.net/opf> ;
    skos:notation "4.4.1.2" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Design logistics network"@en,
        "设计 logistics network"@zh ;
    opf:domain "operating" ;
    opf:level 4 .

<https://oprocess.net/opf/node/4.4.1.3> a skos:Concept,
        opf:ProcessNode ;
    dcterms:source "PCF:4.4.1.3" ;
    skos:broader <https://oprocess.net/opf/node/4.4.1> ;
    skos:definition "Conveying outsourcing needs within the organization, with the objective of sourcing the assistance required. Define the portion of logistical activities that can be transferred to outside suppliers. Assess third-party agencies to carefully select the most appropriate agencies for outsourcing. Convey these needs to management or the appropriate authority."@en,
        "Conveying outsourcing needs within the organization, with the objective of sourcing the assistance required. 定义 the portion of logistical activities that can be transferred to outside suppliers. 评估 third-party agencies to carefully select the most appropriate agencies for outsourcing. Convey these needs to management or the appropriate authority."@zh ;
    skos:inScheme <https://oprocess.net/opf> ;
    skos:notation "4.4.1.3" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Communicate outsourcing needs"@en ;
    opf:domain "operating" ;
    opf:level 4 .

<https://oprocess.net/opf/node/4.4.1.4> a skos:Concept,
        opf:ProcessNode ;
    dcterms:source "PCF:4.4.1.4" ;
    skos:broader <https://oprocess.net/opf/node/4.4.1> ;
    skos:definition "Establishing rules and regulations, as well as the terms and conditions regarding the delivery of service by the company. Develop a delivery plan that specifies what, how, when, and in which way to deliver services to the customer."@en,
        "Establishing rules and regulations, as well as the terms and conditions regarding the delivery of service by the company. 开发 a delivery plan that specifies what, how, when, and in which way to deliver services to the customer."@zh ;
    skos:inScheme <https://oprocess.net/opf> ;
    skos:notation "4.4.1.4" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Develop and maintain delivery service policy"@en,
        "开发 and maintain delivery service policy"@zh ;
    opf:domain "operating" ;
    opf:level 4 .

<https://oprocess.net/opf/node/4.4.1.5> a skos:Concept,
        opf:ProcessNode ;
    dcterms:source "PCF:4.4.1.5" ;
    skos:broader <https://oprocess.net/opf/node/4.4.1> ;
    skos:definition "Optimizing the schedule and costs of transportation services. Design a logistics strategy by strategically creating delivery routes and systems, which optimizes the overall transportation schedules and costs. Evaluate different transportation sources in order to select the most appropriate and cost-effective sources."@en,
        "Optimizing the schedule and costs of transportation services. 设计 a logistics 战略 by strategically creating delivery routes and systems, which optimizes the overall transportation schedules and costs. 评估 different transportation sources in order to select the most appropriate and cost-effective sources."@zh ;
    skos:inScheme <https://oprocess.net/opf> ;
    skos:notation "4.4.1.5" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Optimize transportation schedules and costs"@en,
        "优化 transportation schedules and costs"@zh ;
    opf:domain "operating" ;
    opf:level 4 .

<https://oprocess.net/opf/node/4.4.1.6> a skos:Concept,
        opf:ProcessNode ;
    dcterms:source "PCF:4.4.1.6" ;
    skos:broader <https://oprocess.net/opf/node/4.4.1> ;
    skos:definition "Establishing measures for evaluating the performance of the logistics strategy of the organization. Establish key performance indicators, including the logistics performance index, delivery in full, and delivery on time."@en,
        "Establishing measures for evaluating the 绩效 of the logistics 战略 of the organization. 建立 key 绩效 indicators, including the logistics 绩效 index, delivery in full, and delivery on time."@zh ;
    skos:inScheme <https://oprocess.net/opf> ;
    skos:notation "4.4.1.6" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Define key performance measures"@en,
        "定义 key 绩效 measures"@zh ;
    opf:domain "operating" ;
    opf:level 4 .

