        "Revisioning service delivery procedures that fall short of 绩效 parameters. Realign procedures with specified expectations in order to provide successful service delivery."@zh ;
    skos:inScheme <https://oprocess.net/opf> ;
    skos:notation "5.1.2.6" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Review and validate service delivery procedures"@en,
        "审查 and validate service delivery procedures"@zh ;
    opf:domain "operating" ;
    opf:level 4 .

