<https://oprocess.net/opf/node/6.2.1.1> a skos:Concept,
        opf:ProcessNode ;
    dcterms:source "PCF:6.2.1.1" ;
    skos:broader <https://oprocess.net/opf/node/6.2.1> ;
    skos:definition "Projecting the total workforce required to service customer service inquiries in order to effectively predict the volume of vendor contracts required. Estimate the number of the customer service contracts in an agreed-upon time frame in order to strategically maintain the workforce necessitated for customer inquires. Analyze historical data around customer service contracts, the universe of customer inquiries, frequency of inquiries, servicing capability (per head) of the employees, etc."@en,
        "Projecting the total workforce required to service 客户服务 inquiries in order to effectively predict the volume of vendor contracts required. Estimate the number of the 客户服务 contracts in an agreed-upon time frame in order to strategically maintain the workforce necessitated for customer inquires. 分析 historical data around 客户服务 contracts, the universe of customer inquiries, frequency of inquiries, servicing capability (per head) of the employees, etc."@zh ;
    skos:inScheme <https://oprocess.net/opf> ;
    skos:notation "6.2.1.1" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Forecast volume of customer service contacts"@en,
        "预测 volume of 客户服务 contacts"@zh ;
    opf:domain "operating" ;
    opf:level 4 .

<https://oprocess.net/opf/node/6.2.1.2> a skos:Concept,
        opf:ProcessNode ;
    dcterms:source "PCF:6.2.1.2" ;
    skos:broader <https://oprocess.net/opf/node/6.2.1> ;
    skos:definition "Deploying the workforce to manage customer service contracts. Create a systematic summary of the operations and service required, as well as the specific amount of workforce that is to be deployed to the customer service operations. Ensure workforce is directly proportional to the estimated forecast of customer service contracts."@en,
        "Deploying the workforce to manage 客户服务 contracts. 创建 a systematic summary of the operations and service required, as well as the specific amount of workforce that is to be deployed to the 客户服务 operations. Ensure workforce is directly proportional to the estimated forecast of 客户服务 contracts."@zh ;
    skos:inScheme <https://oprocess.net/opf> ;
    skos:notation "6.2.1.2" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Schedule customer service workforce"@en,
        "调度 客户服务 workforce"@zh ;
    opf:domain "operating" ;
    opf:level 4 .

<https://oprocess.net/opf/node/6.2.1.3> a skos:Concept,
        opf:ProcessNode ;
    dcterms:source "PCF:6.2.1.3" ;
    skos:broader <https://oprocess.net/opf/node/6.2.1> ;
    skos:definition "Tracking the utilization of workforce deployed for managing customer service operations. Monitor the utility of the workforce deployed for managing customer service operations in order to evaluate its efficiency and cost effectiveness. Calculate the overall labor effectiveness, which measures the utility, performance, and quality of the workforce."@en,
        "Tracking the utilization of workforce deployed for managing 客户服务 operations. 监控 the utility of the workforce deployed for managing 客户服务 operations in order to evaluate its efficiency and cost effectiveness. Calculate the overall labor effectiveness, which measures the utility, 绩效, and 质量 of the workforce."@zh ;
    skos:inScheme <https://oprocess.net/opf> ;
    skos:notation "6.2.1.3" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Track workforce utilization"@en,
        "跟踪 workforce utilization"@zh ;
    opf:domain "operating" ;
    opf:level 4 .

<https://oprocess.net/opf/node/6.2.1.4> a skos:Concept,
        opf:ProcessNode ;
    dcterms:source "PCF:6.2.1.4" ;
    skos:broader <https://oprocess.net/opf/node/6.2.1> ;
    skos:definition "Tracking and determining the quality of interactions between the customer and customer representatives. Use technology, including artificial intelligence (AI), to record and effectively assess customer representatives' interactions."@en,
        "Tracking and determining the 质量 of interactions between the customer and customer representatives. Use technology, including 人工智能 (AI), to record and effectively assess customer representatives' interactions."@zh ;
    skos:inScheme <https://oprocess.net/opf> ;
    skos:notation "6.2.1.4" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Monitor and evaluate quality of customer interactions with customer service representatives"@en,
        "监控 and evaluate 质量 of customer interactions with 客户服务 representatives"@zh ;
    opf:domain "operating" ;
    opf:level 4 .

<https://oprocess.net/opf/node/6.2.2.1> a skos:Concept,
        opf:ProcessNode ;
    dcterms:source "PCF:6.2.2.1" ;
    skos:broader <https://oprocess.net/opf/node/6.2.2> ;
    skos:definition "Receiving requests for information from customers over multiple channels. Receive various requests and inquiries from customers regarding products/services. Accept these inquiries through channels such as email, telephone, online forms, text messages, social media, and in person. Supply dedicated equipment, systems, and personnel."@en,
        "Receiving requests for information from customers over multiple channels. 接收 various requests and inquiries from customers regarding products/services. Accept these inquiries through channels such as email, telephone, online forms, text messages, social media, and in person. Supply dedicated equipment, systems, and personnel."@zh ;
    skos:inScheme <https://oprocess.net/opf> ;
    skos:notation "6.2.2.1" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Receive customer problems, requests, and inquiries"@en,
        "接收 customer 问题s, requests, and inquiries"@zh ;
    opf:domain "operating" ;
    opf:level 4 .

<https://oprocess.net/opf/node/6.2.2.2> a skos:Concept,
        opf:ProcessNode ;
    dcterms:source "PCF:6.2.2.2" ;
    skos:broader <https://oprocess.net/opf/node/6.2.2> ;
    skos:definition "Analyzing various requests and inquiries from customers regarding products/services. Provide answers and offerings to satisfy the customer's needs."@en,
        "Analyzing various requests and inquiries from customers regarding products/services. 提供 answers and offerings to satisfy the customer's needs."@zh ;
    skos:inScheme <https://oprocess.net/opf> ;
    skos:notation "6.2.2.2" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Analyze problems, requests, and inquiries"@en,
        "分析 问题s, requests, and inquiries"@zh ;
    opf:domain "operating" ;
    opf:level 4 .

<https://oprocess.net/opf/node/6.2.2.3> a skos:Concept,
        opf:ProcessNode ;
    dcterms:source "PCF:6.2.2.3" ;
    skos:broader <https://oprocess.net/opf/node/6.2.2> ;
    skos:definition "Routing customer inquiries in order to service them with the most apposite response. Direct customer inquires to the best suited personnel or system. Have a system or procedure capable of efficiently channeling these requests."@en ;
    skos:inScheme <https://oprocess.net/opf> ;
    skos:notation "6.2.2.3" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Resolve customer problems, requests, and inquiries"@en,
        "解决 customer 问题s, requests, and inquiries"@zh ;
    opf:domain "operating" ;
    opf:level 4 .

<https://oprocess.net/opf/node/6.2.2.4> a skos:Concept,
        opf:ProcessNode ;
    dcterms:source "PCF:6.2.2.4" ;
    skos:broader <https://oprocess.net/opf/node/6.2.2> ;
    skos:definition "Responding to customer requests by email, conversation, interactive voice response, mail, etc. with the most appropriate reply. Instill a robust process to locate the right information for a solution to a customer's problem."@en,
        "Responding to customer requests by email, conversation, interactive voice response, mail, etc. with the most appropriate reply. Instill a robust process to locate the right information for a solution to a customer's 问题."@zh ;
    skos:inScheme <https://oprocess.net/opf> ;
    skos:notation "6.2.2.4" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Respond to customer problems, requests, and inquiries"@en,
        "Respond to customer 问题s, requests, and inquiries"@zh ;
    opf:domain "operating" ;
    opf:level 4 .

<https://oprocess.net/opf/node/6.2.2.5> a skos:Concept,
        opf:ProcessNode ;
    dcterms:source "PCF:6.2.2.5" ;
    skos:broader <https://oprocess.net/opf/node/6.2.2> ;
    skos:definition "Utilizing customer inquiries as opportunities to either provide a comparable service to the one in question, offer additional complimentary service, or suggest a service that is better than what was initially offered."@en ;
    skos:inScheme <https://oprocess.net/opf> ;
    skos:notation "6.2.2.5" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Identify and capture upsell/cross-sell opportunities"@en,
        "识别 and capture upsell/cross-sell opportunities"@zh ;
    opf:domain "operating" ;
    opf:level 4 .

<https://oprocess.net/opf/node/6.2.2.6> a skos:Concept,
        opf:ProcessNode ;
    dcterms:source "PCF:6.2.2.6" ;
    skos:broader <https://oprocess.net/opf/node/6.2.2> ;
    skos:definition "Providing possible sales leads to the sales team in an effort to garner more business opportunities."@en ;
    skos:inScheme <https://oprocess.net/opf> ;
    skos:notation "6.2.2.6" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Deliver opportunity to sales team"@en ;
    opf:domain "operating" ;
    opf:level 4 .

<https://oprocess.net/opf/node/6.2.3.1> a skos:Concept,
        opf:ProcessNode ;
    dcterms:source "PCF:6.2.3.1" ;
    skos:broader <https://oprocess.net/opf/node/6.2.3> ;
    skos:definition "Receiving any complaints or grievances from customers for the organization's products/services. Receive objections, complaints, and criticism from customers regarding products/services through email, telephone, online forms, text messages, social media, in person, etc. Dedicate equipment, systems, and personnel."@en,
        "Receiving any complaints or grievances from customers for the organization's products/services. 接收 objections, complaints, and criticism from customers regarding products/services through email, telephone, online forms, text messages, social media, in person, etc. Dedicate equipment, systems, and personnel."@zh ;
    skos:inScheme <https://oprocess.net/opf> ;
    skos:notation "6.2.3.1" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Receive customer complaints"@en,
        "接收 customer complaints"@zh ;
    opf:domain "operating" ;
    opf:level 4 .

<https://oprocess.net/opf/node/6.2.3.2> a skos:Concept,
        opf:ProcessNode ;
    dcterms:source "PCF:6.2.3.2" ;
    skos:broader <https://oprocess.net/opf/node/6.2.3> ;
    skos:definition "Routing any complaints or grievances received from customers in order to address them in the most appropriate manner. Direct complaints to the best suited personnel or system. Implement a system or procedure capable of efficiently channeling the various objections, complaints, and criticism from customers over the offerings provided by the organization."@en,
        "Routing any complaints or grievances received from customers in order to address them in the most appropriate manner. Direct complaints to the best suited personnel or system. 实施 a system or procedure capable of efficiently channeling the various objections, complaints, and criticism from customers over the offerings provided by the organization."@zh ;
    skos:inScheme <https://oprocess.net/opf> ;
    skos:notation "6.2.3.2" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Route customer complaints"@en ;
    opf:domain "operating" ;
    opf:level 4 .

<https://oprocess.net/opf/node/6.2.3.3> a skos:Concept,
        opf:ProcessNode ;
    dcterms:source "PCF:6.2.3.3" ;
    skos:broader <https://oprocess.net/opf/node/6.2.3> ;
    skos:definition "Resolving any customer complaints that are deemed to be sound and reasonable. Redress any objections, grievances, and complaints received from customers regarding the offerings provided by the organization. Identify the legitimate complaints, where the situation needs to be appropriately corrected. Deploy personnel who can rectify the issue within a stipulated time frame."@en,
        "Resolving any customer complaints that are deemed to be sound and reasonable. Redress any objections, grievances, and complaints received from customers regarding the offerings provided by the organization. 识别 the legitimate complaints, where the situation needs to be appropriately corrected. 部署 personnel who can rectify the issue within a stipulated time frame."@zh ;
    skos:inScheme <https://oprocess.net/opf> ;
    skos:notation "6.2.3.3" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Resolve customer complaints"@en,
        "解决 customer complaints"@zh ;
    opf:domain "operating" ;
    opf:level 4 .

<https://oprocess.net/opf/node/6.2.3.4> a skos:Concept,
        opf:ProcessNode ;
    dcterms:source "PCF:6.2.3.4" ;
    skos:broader <https://oprocess.net/opf/node/6.2.3> ;
    skos:definition "Responding to customer complaints including all activities necessitated to service any objections, complaints, or grievances with the most appropriate reply. Source the right information to formulate a response that eases the discomfort being experienced by the customer. (Closely coordinate with Resolve customer complaints [10399].)"@en,
        "Responding to customer complaints including all activities necessitated to service any objections, complaints, or grievances with the most appropriate reply. Source the right information to formulate a response that eases the discomfort being experienced by the customer. (Closely coordinate with 解决 customer complaints [10399].)"@zh ;
    skos:inScheme <https://oprocess.net/opf> ;
    skos:notation "6.2.3.4" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Respond to customer complaints"@en ;
    opf:domain "operating" ;
    opf:level 4 .

