    dcterms:source "PCF:7.1.2.13" ;
    skos:broader <https://oprocess.net/opf/node/7.1.2> ;
    skos:definition "Creating and implementing models for effectively strategizing the work force of the organization. Develop a model that specifies the organization's overall approach for maximizing the performance of its work force by defining the goals, objectives, and expectations of the work force. Manage all aspects of performance required for the work force to function, including recruitment, selection, retention, and professional development."@en,
        "Creating and implementing 模型s for effectively strategizing the work force of the organization. 开发 a 模型 that specifies the organization's overall approach for maximizing the 绩效 of its work force by defining the goals, objectives, and expectations of the work force. 管理 all aspects of 绩效 required for the work force to function, including recruitment, selection, retention, and professional development."@zh ;
    skos:inScheme <https://oprocess.net/opf> ;
    skos:notation "7.1.2.13" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Develop workforce strategy models"@en,
        "开发 workforce 战略 模型s"@zh ;
    opf:domain "management_support" ;
    opf:level 4 .

