        "Creating a process to follow in case of a failed payment by account holders. 创建 rules and regulations for the account holder who has failed to make at least the minimum monthly payment by the due date."@zh ;
    skos:inScheme <https://oprocess.net/opf> ;
    skos:notation "9.2.4.1" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Establish policies for delinquent accounts"@en,
        "建立 policies for delinquent accounts"@zh ;
    opf:domain "management_support" ;
    opf:level 4 .

