<https://oprocess.net/opf/node/9.9> a skos:Concept,
        opf:ProcessNode ;
    dcterms:source "PCF:9.9" ;
    skos:broader <https://oprocess.net/opf/node/9.0> ;
    skos:definition "Estimating the organization's periodic tax liabilities. Ensure that appropriate taxing authorities receive tax return filings and payments when due."@en ;
    skos:inScheme <https://oprocess.net/opf> ;
    skos:notation "9.9" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Manage taxes"@en,
        "管理 taxes"@zh ;
    opf:domain "management_support" ;
    opf:level 2 .

<https://oprocess.net/opf/node/1.1.2> a skos:Concept,
        opf:ProcessNode ;
    dcterms:source "PCF:1.1.2" ;
    skos:broader <https://oprocess.net/opf/node/1.1> ;
    skos:definition "Examining the market to identify customer required solutions. Assess the relevant market(s) to determine the products/services that are needed or wanted by customers. Carry out quantitative and qualitative analyses to capture and investigate products/services. Employ creative techniques that allow for a closer appreciation of the customer, and design relevant solutions."@en,
        "Examining the market to identify customer required solutions. 评估 the relevant market(s) to determine the products/services that are needed or wanted by customers. Carry out quantitative and qualitative analyses to capture and investigate products/services. Employ creative techniques that allow for a closer appreciation of the customer, and design relevant solutions."@zh ;
    skos:inScheme <https://oprocess.net/opf> ;
    skos:notation "1.1.2" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Survey market and determine customer needs and wants"@en ;
    opf:domain "operating" ;
    opf:level 3 .

<https://oprocess.net/opf/node/1.1.4> a skos:Concept,
        opf:ProcessNode ;
    dcterms:source "PCF:1.1.4" ;
    skos:broader <https://oprocess.net/opf/node/1.1> ;
    skos:definition "Establishing the organization's long-term vision as a strategic positioning and engagement of stakeholders. Institute the vision by creating strategic orientations of all stakeholders. Understand the strategy development frameworks in this context."@en,
        "Establishing the organization's long-term vision as a strategic positioning and engagement of stakeholders. Institute the vision by creating strategic orientations of all stakeholders. Understand the 战略 development frameworks in this context."@zh ;
    skos:inScheme <https://oprocess.net/opf> ;
    skos:notation "1.1.4" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Establish strategic vision"@en,
        "建立 strategic vision"@zh ;
    opf:domain "operating" ;
    opf:level 3 .

<https://oprocess.net/opf/node/1.1.5> a skos:Concept,
        opf:ProcessNode ;
    dcterms:source "PCF:1.1.5" ;
    skos:broader <https://oprocess.net/opf/node/1.1> ;
    skos:definition "Examining the scope and contingencies for restructuring based on market situation and internal realities. Map the market forces over which any and all probabilities can be probed for utility and viability. Once the restructuring options have been analyzed and the due-diligence performed, execute the deal. Consider seeking professional services for assistance in formalizing these opportunities."@en ;
    skos:inScheme <https://oprocess.net/opf> ;
    skos:notation "1.1.5" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Conduct organization restructuring opportunities"@en,
        "开展 organization restructuring opportunities"@zh ;
    opf:domain "operating" ;
    opf:level 3 .

<https://oprocess.net/opf/node/1.2.1> a skos:Concept,
        opf:ProcessNode ;
    dcterms:source "PCF:1.2.1" ;
    skos:broader <https://oprocess.net/opf/node/1.2> ;
    skos:definition "Establishing an overarching, compact statement that concisely underscores the mission of the organization. Define and communicate a clear and succinct mission statement, which encapsulates how the organization aims to proceed in order to Establish a strategic vision [10020]. Solicit critical inputs from senior management and strategy executives, and collaborate with marketing or personnel from allied functions."@en,
        "Establishing an overarching, compact statement that concisely underscores the mission of the organization. 定义 and communicate a clear and succinct mission statement, which encapsulates how the organization aims to proceed in order to 建立 a strategic vision [10020]. Solicit critical inputs from senior management and 战略 executives, and collaborate with marketing or personnel from allied functions."@zh ;
    skos:inScheme <https://oprocess.net/opf> ;
    skos:notation "1.2.1" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Develop overall mission statement"@en,
        "开发 overall mission statement"@zh ;
    opf:domain "operating" ;
    opf:level 3 .

<https://oprocess.net/opf/node/1.2.6> a skos:Concept,
        opf:ProcessNode ;
    dcterms:source "PCF:1.2.6" ;
    skos:broader <https://oprocess.net/opf/node/1.2> ;
    skos:definition "Developing overall goals for the organization that help in accomplishing its mission. Formulate organization-wide targets in the near to middle term, which will accumulate and propel the organization to realize its long-term objectives, as outlined in Develop an overall mission statement [10037]. Enlist business unit heads or equivalent personnel, in close collaboration with senior management executives."@en,
        "Developing overall goals for the organization that help in accomplishing its mission. Formulate organization-wide targets in the near to middle term, which will accumulate and propel the organization to realize its long-term objectives, as outlined in 开发 an overall mission statement [10037]. Enlist business unit heads or equivalent personnel, in close collaboration with senior management executives."@zh ;
    skos:inScheme <https://oprocess.net/opf> ;
    skos:notation "1.2.6" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Develop and set organizational objectives"@en,
        "开发 and set organizational objectives"@zh ;
    opf:domain "operating" ;
    opf:level 3 .

<https://oprocess.net/opf/node/1.2.7> a skos:Concept,
        opf:ProcessNode ;
    dcterms:source "PCF:1.2.7" ;
    skos:broader <https://oprocess.net/opf/node/1.2> ;
    skos:definition "Charting a strategic course for business units in order to leverage opportunities, sidestep hurdles, and create synergies among each other. Create strategic road maps for the organization's units--in light of their individual resources and requirements, as well as their relationships with other business units--to achieve organizational goals."@en,
        "Charting a strategic course for business units in order to leverage opportunities, sidestep hurdles, and create synergies among each other. 创建 strategic road maps for the organization's units--in light of their individual resources and requirements, as well as their relationships with other business units--to achieve organizational goals."@zh ;
    skos:inScheme <https://oprocess.net/opf> ;
    skos:notation "1.2.7" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Formulate business unit strategies"@en ;
    opf:domain "operating" ;
    opf:level 3 .

<https://oprocess.net/opf/node/1.2.8.1> a skos:Concept,
        opf:ProcessNode ;
    dcterms:source "PCF:1.2.8.1" ;
    skos:broader <https://oprocess.net/opf/node/1.2.8> ;
    skos:definition "Measuring customer feedback in regard to product and services effectiveness based on overall satisfaction. The data to be analyzed is collected through surveys, customer responses, and feedbacks based on the delivered products/services."@en ;
    skos:inScheme <https://oprocess.net/opf> ;
    skos:notation "1.2.8.1" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Assess customer experience"@en,
        "评估 customer experience"@zh ;
    opf:domain "operating" ;
    opf:level 4 .

<https://oprocess.net/opf/node/1.3.1> a skos:Concept,
        opf:ProcessNode ;
    dcterms:source "PCF:1.3.1" ;
    skos:broader <https://oprocess.net/opf/node/1.3> ;
    skos:definition "Developing strategic projects that help fulfill long-term goals. Develop time-bound projects that are discretionary in nature and lie beyond the scope of the organization's routine operations."@en,
        "Developing strategic projects that help 履约 long-term goals. 开发 time-bound projects that are discretionary in nature and lie beyond the scope of the organization's routine operations."@zh ;
    skos:inScheme <https://oprocess.net/opf> ;
    skos:notation "1.3.1" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Develop strategic initiatives"@en,
        "开发 strategic initiatives"@zh ;
    opf:domain "operating" ;
    opf:level 3 .

<https://oprocess.net/opf/node/1.3.4> a skos:Concept,
