    skos:broader <https://oprocess.net/opf/node/1.0> ;
    skos:definition "Establishing how an organization creates, delivers and captures value or makes profit. Identify the products or services that a business will sell, its target market, anticipated expenses, and other core aspects of its modus operandi. Revise the plan as required to reflect changing circumstances."@en,
        "Establishing how an organization creates, delivers and captures value or makes profit. 识别 the products or services that a business will sell, its target market, anticipated expenses, and other core aspects of its modus operandi. Revise the plan as required to reflect changing circumstances."@zh ;
    skos:inScheme <https://oprocess.net/opf> ;
    skos:notation "1.4" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Develop and maintain business models"@en,
