    skos:broader <https://oprocess.net/opf/node/13.2> ;
    skos:definition "Establishing, implementing, and managing business programs. Successfully handle related projects that together constitute a program. Establish the program structure and approach. Coordinate with stakeholders and partners. Execute the program. Assess and report the performance of the program. Coordinate and prioritize resources across projects. Manage links between the projects and the overall costs and risks of the program."@en,
        "Establishing, implementing, and managing business programs. Successfully handle related projects that together constitute a program. 建立 the program structure and approach. 协调 with stakeholders and partners. 执行 the program. 评估 and report the 绩效 of the program. Coordinate and prioritize resources across projects. 管理 links between the projects and the overall costs and 风险s of the program."@zh ;
    skos:inScheme <https://oprocess.net/opf> ;
    skos:notation "13.2.2" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Manage programs"@en,
        "管理 programs"@zh ;
    opf:domain "management_support" ;
    opf:level 3 .

<https://oprocess.net/opf/node/13.3> a skos:Concept,
        opf:ProcessNode ;
    dcterms:source "PCF:13.3" ;
    skos:broader <https://oprocess.net/opf/node/13.0> ;
    skos:definition "Managing organizational attributes that are closely associated with the quality of output. Determine the quality requirements. Evaluate the correspondence between the quality performance and requirements. Manage non-conformance activities. Ensure implementation and maintenance of the enterprise quality management system."@en,
        "Managing organizational attributes that are closely associated with the 质量 of output. Determine the 质量 requirements. 评估 the correspondence between the 质量 绩效 and requirements. 管理 non-conformance activities. Ensure implementation and maintenance of the enterprise 质量 management system."@zh ;
    skos:inScheme <https://oprocess.net/opf> ;
    skos:notation "13.3" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Manage enterprise quality"@en,
        "管理 enterprise 质量"@zh ;
    opf:domain "management_support" ;
    opf:level 2 .

<https://oprocess.net/opf/node/13.3.1.3> a skos:Concept,
        opf:ProcessNode ;
    dcterms:source "PCF:13.3.1.3" ;
    skos:broader <https://oprocess.net/opf/node/13.3.1> ;
    skos:definition "Developing controls for managing the quality of enterprise. Define the process steps for quality controls and the sampling plan. Identify the tools and methods to measure quality. Define the competencies required."@en,
        "Developing controls for managing the 质量 of enterprise. 定义 the process steps for 质量 controls and the sampling plan. 识别 the tools and methods to measure 质量. Define the competencies required."@zh ;
    skos:inScheme <https://oprocess.net/opf> ;
    skos:notation "13.3.1.3" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Develop quality controls"@en,
        "开发 质量 controls"@zh ;
    opf:domain "management_support" ;
    opf:level 4 .

<https://oprocess.net/opf/node/13.3.2.2> a skos:Concept,
        opf:ProcessNode ;
