<https://oprocess.net/opf/node/2.2> a skos:Concept,
        opf:ProcessNode ;
    dcterms:source "PCF:2.2" ;
    skos:broader <https://oprocess.net/opf/node/2.0> ;
    skos:definition "Identifying and describing new product or service thoughts based on organizational objectives/targets."@en ;
    skos:inScheme <https://oprocess.net/opf> ;
    skos:notation "2.2" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Generate and define new product/service ideas"@en ;
    opf:domain "operating" ;
    opf:level 2 .

<https://oprocess.net/opf/node/2.3.2> a skos:Concept,
        opf:ProcessNode ;
    dcterms:source "PCF:2.3.2" ;
    skos:broader <https://oprocess.net/opf/node/2.3> ;
    skos:definition "Expanding on the marketplace analysis that took place earlier in the product development lifecycle by testing the market against offerings. The results from this in-depth analysis will help the organization finalize product/service characteristics and technical requirements and also identify any needed changes in the manufacturing and delivery processes that support market delivery. To prepare a detailed market study that accounts for any changes in the global environment, the organization may want to conduct a series of interviews, workshops, and focus groups with potential and existing customers."@en,
        "Expanding on the marketplace analysis that took place earlier in the product development lifecycle by testing the market against offerings. The results from this in-depth analysis will help the organization finalize product/service characteristics and technical requirements and also identify any needed 变更s in the manufacturing and delivery processes that support market delivery. To prepare a detailed market study that accounts for any 变更s in the global environment, the organization may want to conduct a series of interviews, workshops, and focus groups with potential and existing customers."@zh ;
    skos:inScheme <https://oprocess.net/opf> ;
    skos:notation "2.3.2" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Test market for new or revised products and services"@en,
        "测试 market for new or revised 产品和服务"@zh ;
    opf:domain "operating" ;
    opf:level 3 .

<https://oprocess.net/opf/node/3.1.2> a skos:Concept,
        opf:ProcessNode ;
    dcterms:source "PCF:3.1.2" ;
    skos:broader <https://oprocess.net/opf/node/3.1> ;
    skos:definition "Appraising market opportunities by quantifying and subjecting them to prioritization, as well as validation tests. Closely examine the market opportunities that have been identified by Perform customer and market intelligence analysis [10106]. Triangulate those opportunities to capitalize by finding a fit between identified opportunities and the composite of organizational capabilities and business strategy."@en,
        "Appraising market opportunities by quantifying and subjecting them to prioritization, as well as validation tests. Closely examine the market opportunities that have been identified by Perform customer and market intelligence analysis [10106]. Triangulate those opportunities to capitalize by finding a fit between identified opportunities and the composite of organizational capabilities and business 战略."@zh ;
    skos:inScheme <https://oprocess.net/opf> ;
    skos:notation "3.1.2" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Evaluate and prioritize market opportunities"@en,
        "评估 and prioritize market opportunities"@zh ;
    opf:domain "operating" ;
    opf:level 3 .

<https://oprocess.net/opf/node/3.2.2> a skos:Concept,
        opf:ProcessNode ;
    dcterms:source "PCF:3.2.2" ;
    skos:broader <https://oprocess.net/opf/node/3.2> ;
    skos:definition "Defining and overseeing the positioning, value proposition, and governance of brands to ensure a consistent identity, clear differentiation, and alignment with overall marketing direction and business objectives across markets and offerings."@en,
        "Defining and overseeing the positioning, value proposition, and 治理 of brands to ensure a consistent identity, clear differentiation, and 对齐 with overall marketing direction and business objectives across markets and offerings."@zh ;
    skos:inScheme <https://oprocess.net/opf> ;
    skos:notation "3.2.2" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Develop and manage brands"@en,
        "开发 and manage brands"@zh ;
    opf:domain "operating" ;
    opf:level 3 .

<https://oprocess.net/opf/node/3.2.3> a skos:Concept,
        opf:ProcessNode ;
    dcterms:source "PCF:3.2.3" ;
    skos:broader <https://oprocess.net/opf/node/3.2> ;
    skos:definition "Creating a pricing strategy and mechanism that aligns with the benefits of the products/services, as perceived by customers. Chart a strategic course and a methodology that can guide the pricing of products/services. Draw heavily from the customer value proposition, and balance the expectations of different divisions inside the organization, while delivering the maximum ROI."@en,
        "Creating a pricing 战略 and mechanism that aligns with the benefits of the products/services, as perceived by customers. Chart a strategic course and a methodology that can guide the pricing of products/services. Draw heavily from the customer value proposition, and balance the expectations of different divisions inside the organization, while delivering the maximum ROI."@zh ;
    skos:inScheme <https://oprocess.net/opf> ;
    skos:notation "3.2.3" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Define pricing strategy"@en,
        "定义 pricing 战略"@zh ;
    opf:domain "operating" ;
    opf:level 3 .

<https://oprocess.net/opf/node/3.3.2> a skos:Concept,
        opf:ProcessNode ;
    dcterms:source "PCF:3.3.2" ;
    skos:broader <https://oprocess.net/opf/node/3.3> ;
    skos:definition "Creating a budget for the organization's marketing efforts, in line with the business-wide strategic outlook. Create a plan to distribute resources for achieving the marketing strategy in light of the overall business strategy. Make cost assumptions; calculate the estimated total revenue from the marketing activities against the costs/expenses of these activities. Forecast the return on investment. Attribute costs to the appropriate marketing activities such as promotional campaigns, advertising, marketing communications, PR campaigns, personnel, and office space. Enlist the financial and marketing functions."@en,
        "Creating a budget for the organization's marketing efforts, in line with the business-wide strategic outlook. 创建 a plan to distribute resources for achieving the marketing 战略 in light of the overall business 战略. Make cost assumptions; calculate the estimated total revenue from the marketing activities against the costs/expenses of these activities. 预测 the return on investment. Attribute costs to the appropriate marketing activities such as promotional campaigns, advertising, marketing communications, PR campaigns, personnel, and office space. Enlist the financial and marketing functions."@zh ;
    skos:inScheme <https://oprocess.net/opf> ;
    skos:notation "3.3.2" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Establish marketing budgets"@en,
        "建立 marketing budgets"@zh ;
    opf:domain "operating" ;
    opf:level 3 .

<https://oprocess.net/opf/node/3.3.7> a skos:Concept,
        opf:ProcessNode ;
    dcterms:source "PCF:3.3.7" ;
    skos:broader <https://oprocess.net/opf/node/3.3> ;
    skos:definition "Creating, executing, and administering a strategic road map for packaging products/services. Determine how to package products/services into finished offerings that can be directly marketed to prospective customers. Consider physicality, perishability, and shelf-life. Develop a strategy for packaging products/services. Test alternatives. Collect feedback. Refine the option chosen for execution. Have marketing, product development, and supply chain functions work together to develop sound packaging."@en,
        "Creating, executing, and administering a strategic road map for packaging products/services. Determine how to package products/services into finished offerings that can be directly marketed to prospective customers. Consider physicality, perishability, and shelf-life. 开发 a 战略 for packaging products/services. 测试 alternatives. 收集 feedback. Refine the option chosen for execution. Have marketing, product development, and 供应链 functions work together to develop sound packaging."@zh ;
    skos:inScheme <https://oprocess.net/opf> ;
    skos:notation "3.3.7" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Develop and manage packaging strategy"@en,
        "开发 and manage packaging 战略"@zh ;
    opf:domain "operating" ;
    opf:level 3 .

<https://oprocess.net/opf/node/3.4.1> a skos:Concept,
        opf:ProcessNode ;
    dcterms:source "PCF:3.4.1" ;
    skos:broader <https://oprocess.net/opf/node/3.4> ;
    skos:definition "Developing a sales forecast for the organization's portfolio of offerings, bearing in mind the effect of promotional events, and fine-tuning these in the context of the new forecast. Estimate the future demand for the organization's products/services by analyzing historical information and any promotional activity."@en ;
    skos:inScheme <https://oprocess.net/opf> ;
    skos:notation "3.4.1" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Develop sales forecast"@en,
        "开发 sales forecast"@zh ;
    opf:domain "operating" ;
    opf:level 3 .

<https://oprocess.net/opf/node/3.5.5> a skos:Concept,
        opf:ProcessNode ;
    dcterms:source "PCF:3.5.5" ;
    skos:broader <https://oprocess.net/opf/node/3.5> ;
    skos:definition "Managing the organization's partners and alliances, with the objective of maximizing revenue. Train partners regarding the organization's portfolio of products/services. Craft sales forecasts. Examine their performance. Manage all data held by the organization on these partners."@en,
        "Managing the organization's partners and alliances, with the objective of maximizing revenue. Train partners regarding the organization's portfolio of products/services. Craft sales forecasts. Examine their 绩效. 管理 all data held by the organization on these partners."@zh ;
    skos:inScheme <https://oprocess.net/opf> ;
    skos:notation "3.5.5" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Manage sales partners and alliances"@en,
        "管理 sales partners and alliances"@zh ;
    opf:domain "operating" ;
    opf:level 3 .

